====1.6 L EcoBoost I-4====
1.6L的直列四氣缸EcoBoost引擎首先应用在2009款林肯C概念车上。该发动机调校为180制动马力和244牛.米。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://media.ford.com/article_display.cfm?article_id=29669 |publisher=Ford Motor Company |title=Lincoln C Pairs EcoBoost I-4 with Dual-Clutch Power Shift Transmission for 40-Plus MPG |work=Ford Media |date=January 12, 2009}}</ref>
另外一个150制动马力的1.6L版本发动机将在欧洲市场销售，该发动机具有更低的油耗和更少CO2排放。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://frankfurt2009.fordmedia.eu/documents/johnFleming.pdf |publisher=Ford Motor Company |title=FORD OF EUROPE - FRANKFURT MOTOR SHOW NEWS CONFERENCE SPEECH |work=Ford Media |date=September 15, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720161909/http://frankfurt2009.fordmedia.eu/documents/johnFleming.pdf |archivedate=2011年7月20日 }}</ref>

